    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The conditions of service summarised below apply to all casual workers engaged on a short term basis with the University.</p>
<p>This is not an employment contract and it does not give you any employment rights, other than those to which workers are entitled. You will not be our employee.</p>
<p>This contract is also your written statement of particulars under section 1 of the Employment Rights Act 1996.</p>]]></Value>
